Viking Supply Ships ökade vinsten i tredje kvartalet
Rederiet Viking Supply Ships hade en nettoomsättning för kvarvarande verksamhet på 159 miljoner kronor (72) under det tredje kvartalet.
07 Nov 2019, 07:56 by Nyhetsbyrån Direkt

Viking Supply Ships increased profit in the third quarter
The shipping company Viking Supply Ships had net sales for continuing operations of SEK 159 million (72) during the third quarter.
